Data::RandomKeep version 0.01
================

This module helps you randomly keep a given number of items, for
example, 10 random lines from a file.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires Test::Usage for its tests.

